<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{businessName}} - Plan de Negocio</title>
    <style>
        /* Modern Professional Design System */
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');
        
        :root {
            --primary-emerald: #10B981;
            --primary-emerald-dark: #059669;
            --emerald-light: #D1FAE5;
            --emerald-50: #ECFDF5;
            --gray-900: #111827;
            --gray-800: #1F2937;
            --gray-700: #374151;
            --gray-600: #4B5563;
            --gray-500: #6B7280;
            --gray-400: #9CA3AF;
            --gray-300: #D1D5DB;
            --gray-100: #F3F4F6;
            --gray-50: #F9FAFB;
            --white: #FFFFFF;
            --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            --shadow-md: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            --shadow-lg: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            --radius-md: 8px;
            --radius-lg: 12px;
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--gray-700);
            background: var(--white);
            font-size: 14px;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 210mm;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        /* Typography */
        h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
            color: var(--gray-900);
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-emerald), var(--primary-emerald-dark));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        h2 {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gray-900);
            margin-top: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--emerald-light);
            position: relative;
        }
        
        h2::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -2px;
            left: 0;
            width: 60px;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-emerald), var(--primary-emerald-dark));
        }
        
        h3 {
            font-size: 1.375rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gray-800);
            margin-top: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        h4 {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gray-700);
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }
        
        p {
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--gray-600);
            text-align: justify;
        }
        
        /* Lists */
        ul, ol {
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--gray-600);
        }
        
        ul li::marker {
            color: var(--primary-emerald);
        }
        
        strong {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gray-800);
        }
        
        em {
            font-style: italic;
            color: var(--gray-500);
        }
        
        /* Links */
        a {
            color: var(--primary-emerald);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }
        
        a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-emerald-dark);
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        /* Page breaks */
        .page-break {
            page-break-before: always;
        }
        
        .page-break-avoid {
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }
        
        /* Cover page */
        .cover-page {
            height: 297mm;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--emerald-50) 0%, var(--white) 100%);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .cover-page::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            right: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.03) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: pulse 8s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
        }
        
        .cover-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 3rem;
        }
        
        .cover-title {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-emerald), var(--primary-emerald-dark));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        
        .cover-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--gray-600);
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.025em;
        }
        
        .business-card {
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            padding: 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        
        .business-name {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--gray-900);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .business-meta {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .meta-item {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .meta-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gray-500);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }
        
        .meta-value {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--gray-800);
        }
        
        .generation-info {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--gray-500);
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
        }
        
        .brand-footer {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 3rem;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--gray-400);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }
        
        .brand-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-emerald);
        }
        
        /* Table of contents */
        .toc-container {
            padding: 3rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .toc-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gray-900);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .toc-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .toc-item {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
        }
        
        .toc-link {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            color: var(--gray-700);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
        }
        
        .toc-link:hover {
            background: var(--emerald-50);
            color: var(--primary-emerald-dark);
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .toc-number {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-emerald);
            margin-right: 1rem;
        }
        
        .toc-title-text {
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .toc-dots {
            flex: 1;
            border-bottom: 2px dotted var(--gray-300);
            margin: 0 1rem;
            height: 1px;
        }
        
        /* Content sections */
        .content-page {
            padding: 3rem;
            min-height: 297mm;
        }
        
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        
        .section-content {
            color: var(--gray-600);
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        
        .section-content h3 {
            color: var(--gray-800);
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .section-content h4 {
            color: var(--gray-700);
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }
        
        /* Business info highlight */
        .business-highlight {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--emerald-50), var(--white));
            border: 1px solid var(--emerald-light);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-emerald);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: 2rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .business-highlight::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-emerald), transparent);
        }
        
        .highlight-title {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gray-900);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .highlight-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        
        .highlight-item {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        
        .highlight-label {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gray-500);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }
        
        .highlight-value {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--gray-800);
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        /* Appendix */
        .appendix-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        
        .reference-card {
            background: var(--gray-50);
            border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }
        
        .reference-card:hover {
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
            border-color: var(--emerald-light);
        }
        
        .reference-title {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gray-800);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .reference-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .reference-list li {
            padding: 0.5rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
        }
        
        .reference-list li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .reference-list a {
            color: var(--primary-emerald);
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        /* Footer */
        .document-footer {
            background: var(--gray-50);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
            padding: 2rem 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }
        
        .footer-content {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .footer-brand {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gray-800);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .footer-tagline {
            color: var(--gray-500);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .footer-logo {
            color: var(--primary-emerald);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }
        
        /* Print optimizations */
        @media print {
            body {
                font-size: 12px;
            }
            
            .cover-page {
                height: 100vh;
            }
            
            .content-page {
                padding: 2rem;
            }
            
            .toc-container {
                padding: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Cover Page -->
        <div class="cover-page">
            <div class="cover-content">
                <h1 class="cover-title">Plan de Negocio</h1>
                <p class="cover-subtitle">Estrategia profesional para el éxito empresarial</p>
                
                <div class="business-card">
                    <h2 class="business-name">{{businessName}}</h2>
                    
                    <div class="business-meta">
                        <div class="meta-item">
                            <span class="meta-label">Sector</span>
                            <span class="meta-value">{{businessType}}</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="meta-item">
                            <span class="meta-label">Ubicación</span>
                            <span class="meta-value">{{location}}</span>
                        </div>
                        {{#if targetAudience}}
                        <div class="meta-item">
                            <span class="meta-label">Mercado Objetivo</span>
                            <span class="meta-value">{{targetAudience}}</span>
                        </div>
                        {{/if}}
                    </div>
                    
                    {{#if businessDescription}}
                    <div class="business-highlight">
                        <h3 class="highlight-title">Visión del Proyecto</h3>
                        <p>{{{formatContent businessDescription}}}</p>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    
                    <div class="generation-info">
                        <p><strong>Plan generado:</strong> {{generationDate}}</p>
                        <p>Documento confidencial para uso estratégico interno</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="brand-footer">
                <p>Generado por <span class="brand-name">PlanMaestro</span></p>
                <p>Inteligencia Artificial aplicada a la consultoría empresarial</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Table of Contents -->
        <div class="page-break">
            <div class="toc-container">
                <h2 class="toc-title">Índice de Contenidos</h2>
                <ul class="toc-list">
                    {{#each sections}}
                    <li class="toc-item">
                        <a href="#section-{{@index}}" class="toc-link">
                            <span class="toc-number">{{add @index 1}}.</span>
                            <span class="toc-title-text">{{this.title}}</span>
                            <span class="toc-dots"></span>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    {{/each}}
                    <li class="toc-item">
                        <a href="#appendix" class="toc-link">
                            <span class="toc-number">{{add sections.length 1}}.</span>
                            <span class="toc-title-text">Apéndice y Referencias</span>
                            <span class="toc-dots"></span>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content Sections -->
        {{#each sections}}
        <div class="content-page page-break" id="section-{{@index}}">
            <div class="section page-break-avoid">
                <h2>{{add @index 1}}. {{this.title}}</h2>
                <div class="section-content">
                    {{{formatContent this.content}}}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        {{/each}}

        <!-- Appendix -->
        <div class="content-page page-break" id="appendix">
            <div class="section">
                <h2>{{add sections.length 1}}. Apéndice y Referencias</h2>
                
                <div class="appendix-grid">
                    <div class="reference-card">
                        <h3 class="reference-title">🏛️ Recursos Institucionales</h3>
                        <ul class="reference-list">
                            <li>
                                <strong>Small Business Administration (SBA)</strong><br>
                                <a href="https://www.sba.gov" target="_blank">www.sba.gov</a><br>
                                <small>Recursos, financiación y mentorías para pequeñas empresas</small>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <strong>SCORE - Mentores para América</strong><br>
                                <a href="https://www.score.org" target="_blank">www.score.org</a><br>
                                <small>Mentorías gratuitas de empresarios experimentados</small>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="reference-card">
                        <h3 class="reference-title">🎯 Recursos Específicos del Sector {{businessType}}</h3>
                        <ul class="reference-list">
                            <li>
                                <strong>Asociaciones Profesionales</strong><br>
                                <small>Investigue asociaciones específicas de su industria para networking y recursos especializados</small>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <strong>Regulaciones y Licencias</strong><br>
                                <small>Consulte los requisitos regulatorios específicos en {{location}}</small>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <strong>Análisis de Competencia</strong><br>
                                <small>Utilice herramientas como SimilarWeb, SEMrush, o Ahrefs para investigación de mercado</small>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="reference-card">
                        <h3 class="reference-title">📊 Herramientas de Análisis y Gestión</h3>
                        <ul class="reference-list">
                            <li>
                                <strong>Análisis Financiero</strong><br>
                                <small>QuickBooks, FreshBooks, Wave - para contabilidad y finanzas</small>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <strong>Marketing Digital</strong><br>
                                <small>Google Analytics, Facebook Business, LinkedIn Business</small>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <strong>Gestión de Proyectos</strong><br>
                                <small>Asana, Trello, Monday.com - para organización y seguimiento</small>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Document Footer -->
        <div class="document-footer">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <h3 class="footer-brand">{{businessName}}</h3>
                <p class="footer-tagline">Plan de Negocio Estratégico</p>
                <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-200); margin: 1rem 0;">
                <p class="footer-logo">PlanMaestro</p>
                <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--gray-400); margin-top: 0.5rem;">
                    Este documento ha sido generado usando Inteligencia Artificial avanzada<br>
                    Revisión y validación profesional recomendadas antes de la implementación
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
